{"tid":2002652,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒藤孖女]馮盈盈戴祖儀亂入花叢堆影相 頭痛頭暈作嘔疑中毒","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:36:00.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f3ecade164a341de13d03c6f8cc358b6fc88dc","tid":2002652,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"戴祖儀（Joey）今日在Instagram上載身處粉紅花叢中的照片，開心表示在香港找到櫻花，又笑言︰「只要有童心，櫻花都變成真。」誰知她後來補充︰「喊出嚟，原來依（呢）種花叫<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">夾竹桃</span></span></ins></strong>，係有毒的～大家千祈唔好學我哋去影。」馮盈盈留言致歉︰「對唔住，係我發現棵花先，係我差啲害咗你。」<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈之後在其Instagram出post說︰「昨日幫戴祖儀係（喺）路邊嘅花叢中影相留倩影，心諗行街途中都見到如斯嬌美嘅花，世界真美好，但番（返）到屋企到今朝，又頭痛又作嘔，唔知點解，直至Joey問我︰『你有無頭暈作悶嘅徵狀？』原來，那棵粉紅色的花樹，係有劇毒的夾竹桃。故事教訓：路邊的野花不要採，也不要亂接觸，只遠觀好喇。#差點因為影相而中毒的兩位少女，#無啦啦變咗生死之交 #為藝術豁出去 #大家千萬唔好學」<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈回覆《明報》記者查詢時表示︰「我依家無事喇，多謝關心。應該要食先中毒，所以我應該好輕微。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200503/1588515259204/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E6%88%B4%E7%A5%96%E5%84%80%E4%BA%82%E5%85%A5%E8%8A%B1%E5%8F%A2%E5%A0%86%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8-%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B%E9%A0%AD%E6%9A%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%98%94%E7%96%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200503%2F1588515259204%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259B%2588%25E7%259B%2588%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2584%2580%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%258F%25A2%25E5%25A0%2586%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2597%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%259A%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2598%2594%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=05201e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200503%2F1588515259204%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259B%2588%25E7%259B%2588%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2584%2580%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%258F%25A2%25E5%25A0%2586%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2597%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%259A%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2598%2594%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592&h=7f333b7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200503/1588515259204/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E6%88%B4%E7%A5%96%E5%84%80%E4%BA%82%E5%85%A5%E8%8A%B1%E5%8F%A2%E5%A0%86%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8-%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B%E9%A0%AD%E6%9A%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%98%94%E7%96%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92</a>"},{"pid":"8f5f01c175d5a88b39928a6a6137d2312f5742c3","tid":2002652,"uid":248299,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"爸爸的花兒落了"},{"pid":"9bcae5cc4f75a9b26fbac0bb7283e39885031970","tid":2002652,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"諗起連登仔老母食樹葉中咗grayanotoxin"},{"pid":"c8126b6baf5bb119955b7812fed03431ef3fbe43","tid":2002652,"uid":118700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"花吃了這女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34abda3b51a065ad54d9e6248f240d088d810cb","tid":2002652,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8126b6baf5bb119955b7812fed03431ef3fbe43","tid":2002652,"uid":118700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"花吃了這女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"吃了屎的女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}